<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>D.E.T System | Algorithmic Trading</title>

    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@100;300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
    <link href="/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/fontawesome.css">

    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #1a1818;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding-top: 100px; /* Space for fixed header */
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* =========================================
           CUSTOM NEUTRAL NAVBAR
        ========================================= */
        .custom-navbar {
            background-color: #322C2C;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 18px 0;
        }
        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .text-logo {
            color: #B0BF96;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .text-logo span {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 300;
        }
        .text-logo:hover {
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .nav-menu {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            gap: 30px;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .nav-menu li a {
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .nav-menu li a:hover, .nav-menu li a.active {
            color: #B0BF96;
        }
        .nav-btn {
            background: transparent;
            color: #B0BF96 !important;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border: 1px solid #B0BF96;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600 !important;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .nav-btn:hover {
            background: #B0BF96;
            color: #322C2C !important;
        }
        .mobile-toggle {
            display: none;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 28px;
            cursor: pointer;
            user-select: none;
        }

        /* Mobile Menu Responsiveness */
        @media (max-width: 991px) {
            .nav-menu {
                display: none;
                flex-direction: column;
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                background-color: #322C2C;
                padding: 20px 0;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
                text-align: center;
            }
            .nav-menu.active {
                display: flex;
            }
            .nav-menu li {
                padding: 10px 0;
            }
            .mobile-toggle {
                display: block;
            }
        }

        /* =========================================
           HERO DASHBOARD SECTION
        ========================================= */
        .dashboard-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 50px;
        }
        .hero-content {
            flex: 1;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(176, 191, 150, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(176, 191, 150, 0.3);
            color: #B0BF96;
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .status-badge i { margin-right: 8px; font-size: 10px; }

        .hero-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero-title span { color: #B0BF96; }

        .hero-text {
            color: #aaa;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            max-width: 90%;
        }

        /* User Info Block */
        .user-info-block {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-left: 3px solid #B0BF96;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
        }
        .info-item h6 {
            color: #888;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .info-item p {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .det-id { color: #B0BF96 !important; font-family: monospace; font-size: 18px !important;}

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .btn-primary-action {
            background: #B0BF96;
            color: #322C2C;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 15px;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-primary-action:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); color: #1a1818; }

        .btn-secondary-action {
            background: transparent;
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-secondary-action:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color: #fff;}

        /* =========================================
           GLASS WIDGET (Right Side)
        ========================================= */
        .widget-panel {
            flex: 0 0 400px;
            background: #322C2C;
            border: 1px solid rgba(176, 191, 150, 0.2);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }
        .widget-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        .widget-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .widget-title i { color: #B0BF96; }
        .ai-badge {
            background: rgba(176, 191, 150, 0.15);
            color: #B0BF96;
            font-size: 11px;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .data-label {
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #777;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            display: block;
        }
        .data-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        .pulse-text {
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { opacity: 0.6; }
            50% { opacity: 1; }
            100% { opacity: 0.6; }
        }

        .action-box {
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .status-dot {
            height: 10px; width: 10px;
            background-color: #B0BF96;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 8px;
        }

        /* Mobile Adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 991px) {
            .dashboard-container { flex-direction: column; gap: 40px; margin: 40px auto; }
            .widget-panel { flex: auto; width: 100%; }
            .hero-title { font-size: 38px; }
            .action-buttons { flex-direction: column; }
            .user-info-block { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- ***** Custom Navbar Start ***** -->
    <header class="custom-navbar">
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a href="/" class="text-logo">D.E.T <span>SYSTEM</span></a>
            <div class="mobile-toggle" id="mobile-toggle">☰</div>
            <ul class="nav-menu" id="nav-menu">
                <li><a href="/" class="active">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/pricing">Trading Levels</a></li>
                <li><a href="/login">Client Access</a></li>
                <li><a href="/pricing" class="nav-btn">Get Started</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>
    <!-- ***** Custom Navbar End ***** -->

    <!-- MAIN DASHBOARD -->
    <div class="dashboard-container">

        <!-- Left Side: User Details & Actions -->
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="status-badge">
                <i class="fas fa-circle"></i> Status: D.E.T Is Ready
            </div>

            <h1 class="hero-title">
                Welcome to your<br>
                <span>Trading Environment</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="hero-text">
                Your D.E.T is ready. The CornerStore interface connects directly to your MT5, executing precision data analytics and instantly translating them to your personal custody account.
            </p>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="/pricing" class="btn-primary-action">
                    <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Get Started
                </a>
                <a href="/login" class="btn-secondary-action">
                    Client Access
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Side: The Glass Connection Widget -->
        <div class="widget-panel">
            <div class="widget-header">
                <div class="widget-title">
                    <i class="fas fa-network-wired"></i> CornerStore Feed
                </div>
                <div class="ai-badge">System Active</div>
            </div>

            <span class="data-label">Current Trading Asset</span>
            <div class="data-value pulse-text" style="color: #ccc; font-size: 20px;">
                Awaiting Connection...
            </div>

            <span class="data-label">Live Market Price</span>
            <div class="data-value">0.00</div>

            <div class="action-box">
                <span class="data-label">Current Algo Action</span>
                <div style="color: #B0BF96; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin-top: 8px;">
                    <span class="status-dot"></span> Protected State
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
                Activate D.E.T On Your Trading Chart to sync real-time analytics.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script>
        // Mobile Menu Toggle Logic
        document.getElementById('mobile-toggle').addEventListener('click', function() {
            document.getElementById('nav-menu').classList.toggle('active');
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>